<br>
Now take a 6 second cast spell.  After the ring haste it would be down to 5.1 second cast time, 7.6 to chain cast, 8.5 normaly.  Thats about a 9.5% haste overall.  VI just did not think it over, assumed it would be the same as melee weapons where faster=more damage, but the haste works the opposite ways, and in all reality, the 3 second cast time restriction should be removed. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=526560" target="top"> Arch Convoker Kalahad Thundersoul</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
